title: Keen Awards 2004 Winners!
content:
1: Programming
1.1: Best Mod of an original Keen game
Xky's Episode Dash [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/1.1.jpg[/img]
1.2: Best Fan-game
z-1's Keen engine/game project [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/1.2.jpg[/img]
1.3: Best Editor/Other Keen Program
adurdin's new MODKEEN (Keen 4-6) [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/1.3.jpg[/img]

2: Fan Art
2.1: Best Graphical Artwork
DSL's work on the 3d Keen movie [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/2.1.jpg[/img]
2.2: Best Narrative/Song
"man sieht sich galaxie" by analoq [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/2.2.jpg[/img]
2.4: Best Non-Computerized Art
RocketJess: 24HoK Entry, cooking [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/2.3.jpg[/img]


3: Web
3.1: Best Website (judged on content, layout, usability, usefulness, aesthetics...)
Spatang.com's Beyond the Pogo [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/3.1.jpg[/img]
3.3: Forum crew recognition
eK [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/3.3.jpg[/img]


4: Miscellaneous
4.1: Keenest person of the year
Xky [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/4.1.jpg[/img]
4.2: Really Keen Stuff (something great that came out of the blue)
Birdman Demo [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/4.2.jpg[/img]
4.3: Most promising project
Z-1's game [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/4.3.jpg[/img]

5: Special Category
5.0: Best 3/14 Minimod
Norp 3.5: The Maze of Doom by xtraverse [img]http://dosclassics.com/keen/trophies/2004/5.0.jpg[/img]

Congrats to all the winners![img]http://public.clunet.edu/~ebuckle/yorpylogo.jpg[/img]
